  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Is the use of fetal membrane (human amnion) as a transient wound coverage in wound repair
      safe and efficacious.

      Will the incorporation of liposomal gene constructs to amnion enhance the functionality of
      human amnion and improve wound repair.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
